"Vampire Diaries" executive producer Julie Plec will write the episode and serve as showrunner on the new project if it earns a series order.

Leslie Morgenstein and Gina Girolamo will also serve as executive producers. "Vampire Diaries" showrunner Kevin Williamson, who also has his upcoming Fox show "The Following," is not involved with the spinoff.

